data.description: ** FANTASTIC OPPORTUNITY FOR A VACATION HOME / AIRBnB / PRIMARY RESIDENCE !! **  This gorgeous 4 bedroom 3.5 bath home is move in ready and waiting for a new owner!! There are only 38 homes in the small private community that is located 20 MINUTES TO DISNEY AND THE PARKS making it a perfect option for RENTAL OR AIRBnB, as SHORT TERM RENTAL IS ALLOWED !! The home is approx. 3 miles from I-4 and Posner Park which has all the shopping and restaurants you could ask for! The home is also close to Lakeland and only minutes to the Heart of Florida Hospital. Inside on the first floor you will find a very well cared for home with formal dining room, large kitchen with QUARTZ countertops and solid wood custom cabinets with crown molding, and large great room with tile flooring, as well as a half bath. This home also BOAST 2 PRIMARY BEDROOMS, 1 UPSTAIRS AND 1 DOWNSTAIRS!!!  All the windows have been replaced with double hung hurricaine rated ones in 2021...ROOF REPLACED 2018...POOL HEATER REPLACED 2019...VINYL FENCE INSTALLED 2019. Upstairs you will find the 2nd primary bedroom with en-suite bath and 2 more large bedroom with a Jack-n-Jill bath. Also upstairs there is a loft that can be used as an office / playroom / additional sleeping area for guests...MAKING IT POSSIBLE TO SLEEP 8-10 PEOPLE if needed!!  Out back you will find a beautiful in ground pool and lanai all screened in and fenced in surrounded by artificial "K-9" turf for basically no maintenance!! MANY MORE UPDATES TOO!!  This is an amazing chance to get a home that is as versatile as it is beautiful!!
